@startuml
title Level 1 Sequence Diagram (SD) - REGISTER/ADD User Story
autonumber

actor ":User" as User
participant ":System" as System

User -> System: Submits form to create new resource
activate System

alt Resource is added successfully
    System -->> User: Shows success toast and redirects/updates view
else Invalid data provided (e.g., missing fields, validation errors)
    System -->> User: Shows error toast: Invalid data / Business rule violation
else A related resource does not exist
    System -->> User: Shows error toast: Related resource not found
end

deactivate System

@enduml